item.title: CVE-2020-2092|2024-08-04T06:54:00.596Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20robot%20framework%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Robot Framework Plugin 2.0.0 and earlier does not configure its XML parser to prevent XML external entity (XXE) attacks, allowing users with Job/Configure to have Jenkins parse crafted XML documents.
